Step 1
------
Make project folders 
/opt/vlab/

$> sudo mkdir /opt/vlab
$> cd /opt/vlab

Step 2
------
Download <source-archive.tgz> from GitHub && Extract project python files.

$>sudo wget --no-check-certificate https://github.com/mvimplis2013/port_scanner/tree/master/vibm/nomads/archives/nomads_dev.tgz
$>tar -xvzf nomads_dev.tgz